<div class="about-image" id="w-node-_983a1efe-bc5a-123a-d39d-08d6fbd45f8d-465d100c" ><OptimizedImage alt="About Image 02" class="cover-image" loading="eager" src="/images/about-image-02.jpg"/></div>
